Purpose: This is the core paywall enforcement for the guest management page — Import, Export, Add Guest (at limit), Send Message, and bulk Export all gate behind the upgrade prompt for draft events.
Output: Dashboard.tsx with conditional intercepts at all 5 button handlers.
</objective>

